00:57:27,992 --> 00:57:30,460
Why's everyone disappearing?

431
00:57:46,611 --> 00:57:49,944
Oh, hello, this is
Sunny Plant Sales calling

432
00:57:51,015 --> 00:57:52,949
Thank you for your business

433
00:57:53,284 --> 00:57:56,913
Is our boss there
with you by any chance?

434
00:57:58,823 --> 00:58:02,953
Oh, I see... Thank you, and excuse me

435
00:58:07,165 --> 00:58:08,393
I'll go look for him

436
00:58:09,200 --> 00:58:11,168
Wait, Junco, wait

437
00:58:17,575 --> 00:58:18,735
Yes, hello...

438
00:58:23,081 --> 00:58:24,343
Boss?

439
00:58:25,984 --> 00:58:27,713
Help

440
00:58:29,053 --> 00:58:30,213
Yabe!

441
00:58:32,424 --> 00:58:33,948
Are you Yabe?

442
00:58:37,095 --> 00:58:38,528
Yabe!

443
00:58:48,440 --> 00:58:51,102
Help me...

444
00:59:02,320 --> 00:59:09,249
Help me...

445
00:59:12,130 --> 00:59:19,298
Help...

446
00:59:23,308 --> 00:59:25,902
Help...

