01:02:04,869 --> 01:02:07,702
Help me...

456
01:02:07,839 --> 01:02:09,204
Junco!

457
01:02:10,008 --> 01:02:13,000
Look, I'm right here

458
01:02:13,411 --> 01:02:16,073
I'm right here, it's OK

459
01:02:40,738 --> 01:02:41,898
Excuse me

460
01:03:13,638 --> 01:03:16,732
Karasawa Harue tel: 090-4079-2677

