and so are you, Harue

506
01:10:01,612 --> 01:10:03,341
That's for sure, right?

507
01:10:04,915 --> 01:10:09,648
So I don't want to think about
the fact we'll die someday

508
01:10:11,989 --> 01:10:13,718
Just maybe...

509
01:10:13,858 --> 01:10:17,225
In 10 years, or at least
while we're still alive,

510
01:10:17,595 --> 01:10:20,325
