529
01:11:55,593 --> 01:11:57,322
Help...

530
01:11:59,230 --> 01:12:01,596
Help...

531
01:13:05,796 --> 01:13:09,323
Junco, It'll be OK

532
01:13:09,867 --> 01:13:11,801
It'll be OK

533
01:13:12,469 --> 01:13:14,460
