01:23:57,580 --> 01:23:59,070
Harue!

585
01:25:18,194 --> 01:25:20,526
The Forbidden Room

586
01:26:17,387 --> 01:26:19,287
Construction Materials - red tape

587
01:28:11,601 --> 01:28:13,535
I'm...

588
01:28:16,439 --> 01:28:18,168
Not alone...

589
01:28:37,727 --> 01:28:39,160
Harue,

590
01:28:39,295 --> 01:28:41,627
it's me, Kawashima

591
01:28:44,767 --> 01:28:47,736
Harue! Listen!

592
01:28:49,539 --> 01:28:52,736
Listen, what do you say to this?

593
01:28:53,209 --> 01:28:55,803
The two of us live together

594
01:28:56,012 --> 01:28:59,072
That way, we can always be together

595
01:28:59,882 --> 01:29:03,010
If we keep living alone,

596
01:29:03,186 --> 01:29:06,644
we'll just get worse and worse
because we're weak

597
01:29:07,023 --> 01:29:09,457
We'll balance each other out

598
01:29:09,759 --> 01:29:12,159
How about living that way?

599
01:29:12,528 --> 01:29:14,621
Would you try it with me?

600
01:29:14,764 --> 01:29:17,858
What do you think, Harue?!

601
01:29:27,410 --> 01:29:28,206
Harue!

602
01:29:29,479 --> 01:29:30,810
Harue!

603
01:29:32,282 --> 01:29:33,442
Harue!

